How to Open an Account

You can start trading across our award-winning trading platform in a few simple steps: complete our application form, verify your identity and deposit funds. It is as easy as that.
Open Account

Get Started Quickly With These Easy to Follow Steps Below

STEP 1: Register

Fill in the requested fields regarding your personal information to complete Secure Client Portal registration.

STEP 2: Confirm Your Email

Check your email and click on the confirmation link to complete your registration.

STEP 3: Start Your Application

After confirming your email registration link, you will be granted access to the Secure Client Portal. Here you can start filling out the application. We only ask questions that are relevant to your application and for regulatory purposes.

STEP 4: Verify Your Profile

After completing your application, the next step is to upload the necessary documents to finish verifying your profile.

• Proof of identity
• Proof of Address

Click here to see more about our ID requirements.

STEP 5: Open Live Account

You will receive an email after your profile has been completely verified. Access the Secure Client Portal to open your live trading account. Click ‘+ Open New Account’ to get this started. After your new account is created, you may deposit funds and start trading.
